LOG file design
FIELDS:		ID	DATE	TIME	IP	QUERYNAME	STATUS	ACS(access code)	PARAM
CONTENT:	total+1	date	time	REMOTE_ADDR	userqueryname	queued/running/finished/aborted	UYT7UJH89	input=;plot=;anno=;

